statements: SELECT * FROM DiversityInclusivityAI
SELECT dataset_name, inclusivity_score, diversity_score FROM DiversityInclusivityAI
SELECT dataset_name, creator, date_created FROM DiversityInclusivityAI ORDER BY date_created DESC
SELECT * FROM DiversityInclusivityAI WHERE inclusivity_score > 4.5 AND diversity_score < 3.0
SELECT creator, dataset_name FROM DiversityInclusivityAI WHERE dataset_description LIKE '%diversity%'
SELECT * FROM DiversityInclusivityAI WHERE inclusivity_score > 4 AND diversity_score < 3 ORDER BY date_created DESC;
SELECT dataset_name, dataset_description, creator FROM DiversityInclusivityAI WHERE inclusivity_score BETWEEN 3.5 AND 4.5 ORDER BY inclusivity_score DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT creator FROM DiversityInclusivityAI WHERE diversity_score > 4 GROUP BY creator ORDER BY inclusivity_score, diversity_score DESC;
SELECT dataset_name, AVG(inclusivity_score) AS avg_inclusivity_score FROM DiversityInclusivityAI GROUP BY dataset_name HAVING AVG(inclusivity_score) > 3 ORDER BY avg_inclusivity_score DESC;
SELECT dataset_name, diversity_score FROM DiversityInclusivityAI WHERE creator = 'John Doe' AND inclusivity_score < 2 ORDER BY dataset_name ASC, diversity_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM diversity_inclusivity_ai_training_datasets;
SELECT dataset_name, publication_date FROM diversity_inclusivity_ai_training_datasets ORDER BY publication_date DESC;
SELECT id, dataset_name, diversity_score FROM diversity_inclusivity_ai_training_datasets WHERE inclusivity_score > 0.5;
SELECT user_name, user_email FROM dataset_users WHERE user_role = 'researcher';
SELECT * FROM dataset_users ORDER BY user_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM diversity_inclusivity_ai_training_datasets WHERE diversity_score > 0.8;
SELECT dataset_name, publication_date FROM diversity_inclusivity_ai_training_datasets WHERE inclusivity_score < 0.5 ORDER BY publication_date DESC;
SELECT dataset_name, diversity_score, inclusivity_score FROM diversity_inclusivity_ai_training_datasets WHERE diversity_score BETWEEN 0.5 AND 0.7 AND inclusivity_score > 0.3;
SELECT * FROM diversity_inclusivity_ai_training_datasets WHERE publication_date >= '2022-01-01' AND inclusivity_score IS NOT NULL ORDER BY inclusivity_score DESC, diversity_score ASC;
SELECT user_name, user_role FROM dataset_users WHERE user_role = 'admin';

SELECT * FROM dataset_annotations ORDER BY annotation_date DESC

SELECT * FROM ai_training_datasets WHERE diversity_score > 0.8
SELECT dataset_name, inclusivity_score FROM ai_training_datasets WHERE inclusivity_score < 0.5 ORDER BY inclusivity_score DESC
SELECT dataset_name, dataset_description, annotation_text FROM ai_training_datasets JOIN dataset_annotations ON ai_training_datasets.id = dataset_annotations.dataset_id
SELECT contributor_name, contributor_email FROM dataset_contributors WHERE contribution_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31'

SELECT dataset_name, diversity_score FROM ai_training_datasets ORDER BY diversity_score DESC;
SELECT dataset_name, inclusivity_score FROM ai_training_datasets WHERE inclusivity_score > 0.8;
SELECT d.dataset_name, l.label_name FROM ai_training_datasets d JOIN dataset_labels l ON d.dataset_id = l.dataset_id;
SELECT u.user_name, u.role, d.dataset_name FROM dataset_users u JOIN ai_training_datasets d ON u.dataset_id = d.dataset_id WHERE u.role = 'admin';
